---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'About Me';
const description = 'About Stefen Phelps and his skills, interests, etc.';
const permalink = 'https://stefenphelps.com/about';
---

<Layout {title} {description} {permalink}>
	<div class="wrapper about-page">
		<article>
			<h1 style="margin: 0;">{title}</h1>
			<form>
				<h2>Type of info:</h2>
				<div>
					<input type="radio" name="type-of-about" id="professional" value="professional" checked />
					<label for="professional">Professional</label>
				</div>
				<div>
					<input type="radio" name="type-of-about" id="personal" value="personal" />
					<label for="personal">Personal</label>
				</div>
			</form>
			<div class="professional-content active">
				<p>
					Here is a summary of my web development skill&thinsp;/&thinsp;experience and my professional work history.
				</p>
				<h2 class="h3" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Skillset</h2>
				<div class="grid">
					<div class="grid-item">
						<h3 class="h5">Base</h3>
						<label for="html">HTML / HTTP</label>
						<progress id="html" value="99" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="css">CSS / Sass</label>
						<progress id="css" value="95" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="js">JS / TS</label>
						<progress id="js" value="90" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="php">PHP</label>
						<progress id="php" value="84" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="hubl">HubL / Twig</label>
						<progress id="hubl" value="95" max="100"></progress>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item">
						<h3 class="h5">Tools</h3>
						<label for="adobe">NPM / Composer</label>
						<progress id="adobe" value="95" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="hubspot">HubSpot</label>
						<progress id="hubspot" value="99" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="firebase">Firebase</label>
						<progress id="firebase" value="73" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="wordpress">WordPress</label>
						<progress id="wordpress" value="97" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="netlify">Netlify</label>
						<progress id="netlify" value="77" max="100"></progress>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item">
						<h3 class="h5">Libraries</h3>
						<label for="react">(p)React / Next.js</label>
						<progress id="react" value="65" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="vue">Vue / Nuxt.js</label>
						<progress id="vue" value="72" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="angular">Angular</label>
						<progress id="angular" value="55" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="jquery">jQuery</label>
						<progress id="jquery" value="88" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="timber">Timber</label>
						<progress id="timber" value="98" max="100"></progress>
					</div>
				</div>
				<h2 class="h3">Career History</h2>
				<ol>
					<li><time>2021</time> 40% growth at Kelp!</li>
					<li>
						<time>2020</time> Started <a href="https://twitter.com/stefen/status/1300455802147409920">StonkLights</a>.
					</li>
					<li><time>2019</time> Helped grow Kelp to 5 people.</li>
					<li>
						<time>2018</time> Started creative agency Kelp and working for myself full time.
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2017</time> Created and launched Spinstak's custom eCommerce platform first responsive designs.
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2016</time> Started working for Marketing Agency SMS in Brooksville, FL.
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2015</time> Help grow Bluleadz from 7 employees to 17+ employees.
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2014</time> Started working for Inbound Marketing Agency Bluleadz in Tampa, FL.
					</li>
					<li><time>2013</time> Promoted to Web Designer Team Lead</li>
					<li>
						<time>2012</time> First full-time position as a Junior Web Designer in Tampa, FL.
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2011</time> Started Stefen Phelps Web Design and doing freelance work on a frequent basis.
					</li>
					<li><time>2009</time> First (paid) website gig.</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
			<div class="personal-content">
				<p>Here's some random things, foods, and places I enjoy along with some major events in my life.</p>
				<h2 class="h3" style="margin-bottom: 0;">Random things</h2>
				<div class="grid">
					<div class="grid-item">
						<h3 class="h5">Activities</h3>
						<label for="golf">🥏 Disc Golf</label>
						<progress id="golf" value="90" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="racquetball">🏸 Racquetball</label>
						<progress id="racquetball" value="85" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="movies">🏂 Snowboarding</label>
						<progress id="movies" value="91" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="fish">🐟 Fishing</label>
						<progress id="fish" value="65" max="100"></progress>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item">
						<h3 class="h5">Foods I like</h3>
						<label for="tacos">🌮 Tacos</label>
						<progress id="tacos" value="97" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="sushi">🍣 Sushi</label>
						<progress id="sushi" value="74" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="cucs">🥒 Cucumbers</label>
						<progress id="cucs" value="16" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="gyros">🥙 Gyros</label>
						<progress id="gyros" value="85" max="100"></progress>
					</div>
					<div class="grid-item">
						<h3 class="h5">Places&thinsp;/&thinsp;Times</h3>
						<label for="beaches">🏖 Beaches</label>
						<progress id="beaches" value="45" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="mountains">🏔 Mountains</label>
						<progress id="mountains" value="92" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="fall">🍁 Fall</label>
						<progress id="fall" value="85" max="100"></progress>
						<label for="spring">🌼 Spring</label>
						<progress id="spring" value="70" max="100"></progress>
					</div>
				</div>
				<h2 class="h3">Personal Milestones</h2>
				<ol>
					<li>
						<time>2021</time> Minivan owner achievement unlocked.
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2020</time> 10 years married!
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2019</time> Made another baby and moved into new home.
					</li>
					<li>
						<time>2018</time> Sold our house and start building process.
					</li>
					<li><time>2017</time> Made another baby.</li>
					<li><time>2015</time> Made another baby.</li>
					<li><time>2013</time> Made a baby.</li>
					<li><time>2011</time> Bought a house.</li>
					<li><time>2010</time> Moved to Florida and got married.</li>
					<li><time>2008</time> Associates degree.</li>
					<li><time>2006</time> Graduated high school.</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
			<p style="margin-top: 3rem;">
				If you'd like to learn more about what I'm into go check out some of
				<a href="/blog/">my writing</a>.
			</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</Layout>
